item.description: First public release of otel4s, an OpenTelemetry implementation for Cats Effect. otel4s aims to be a full and faithful impemenation of the OpenTelemetry Specification, built for the idioms of the Typelevel ecosystem. https://github.com/typelevel/otel4s/discussions/121 #Otel4s #Typelevel #Scala #OpenTelemetry #CatsEffect
